.Dd $Mdocdate: April 18 2012 $
.Dt PANEL 4 sgi
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm panel
.Nd front-panel buttons
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "panel* at hpc?"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
driver handles the front-panel power and, on Indy, volume buttons.
If the
.Va hw.allowpowerdown
.Xr sysctl 8
is set to 1,
.Nm
will signal
.Xr init 8
to do a clean
.Xr shutdown 8
when the power button is pressed.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr hpc 4 ,
.Xr intro 4 ,
.Xr init 8 ,
.Xr rc.shutdown 8 ,
.Xr sysctl 8
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Nm
driver first appeared in
.Ox 5.2 .
.\" .Sh AUTHORS
.\" The
.\" .Nm
.\" driver was written by
.\" .An Miod Vallat .
@


